sp.p:
The honour of God requires the worship
of his Images, for that redounds to God;
as if I honour a Prince, I will honour his Picture;
and we shew our reverence to the King
in being uncovered in his Presence Chamber,
though the King be not there.

div.p:
Fourthly, That the work be perfect;
for that action which needs a pardon, certainly
cannot deserve a reward.
